9.9, 1324.9]}, {"text": "25", "bbox": [1029.8, 1305.9, 1047.1, 1324.9]}, {"text": "0.8", "bbox": [1129.6, 1305.9, 1151.2, 1324.9]}, {"text": "Wisconsin", "bbox": [154.5, 1327.1, 240.1, 1346.2]}, {"text": "20", "bbox": [864.5, 1327.1, 881.7, 1346.2]}, {"text": "2.9", "bbox": [938.3, 1327.1, 959.9, 1346.2]}, {"text": "30", "bbox": [1029.8, 1327.1, 1047.1, 1346.2]}, {"text": "0.7", "bbox": [1129.6, 1327.1, 1151.2, 1346.2]}, {"text": "% of total", "bbox": [911.9, 835.8, 984.0, 854.8]}, {"text": "earned", "bbox": [922.9, 857.6, 968.7, 876.7]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [1106.3, 813.8, 1168.5, 832.8]}, {"text": "premium per", "bbox": [1091.1, 835.8, 1183.5, 854.8]}, {"text": "location", "bbox": [1107.5, 857.6, 1163.1, 876.7]}, {"text": "Earned", "bbox": [841.3, 835.8, 894.4, 854.8]}, {"text": "premiums", "bbox": [831.6, 857.6, 899.7, 876.7]}, {"text": "Agency", "bbox": [1009.4, 835.8, 1066.4, 854.8]}, {"text": "locations", "bbox": [1004.6, 857.6, 1066.8, 876.7]}, {"text": "PERSONAL LINES PROPERTY CASUALTY INSURANCE SEGMENT", "bbox": [187.5, 61.3, 942.2, 93.5]}, {"text": "The personal lines property casualty insurance segment contributed net earned premiums of $685 million", "bbox": [187.5, 97.8, 1137.2, 121.4]}, {"text": "to total revenues, or 17.6 percent of the total, and reported a loss before income taxes of $81 million in", "bbox": [187.5, 121.4, 1114.6, 145.0]}, {"text": "2009. Personal lines net earned premiums declined 0.6 percent in 2009, 3.4 percent in 2008 and", "bbox": [187.5, 145.0, 1066.4, 168.7]}, {"text": "6.3 percent in 2007.", "bbox": [187.5, 168.6, 381.0, 192.3]}, {"text": "We prefer to write personal lines coverage in accounts that include both auto and homeowner coverages as", "bbox": [187.5, 198.5, 1149.1, 222.2]}, {"text": "well as coverages that are part of our other personal business line. As a result, we believe that our personal", "bbox": [187.5, 222.1, 1145.8, 245.8]}, {"text": "lines business is best measured and evaluated on a segment basis. However, we provide line of business", "bbox": [187.5, 245.8, 1125.2, 269.4]}, {"text": "data to summarize growth and profitability trends separately for three business lines:", "bbox": [187.5, 269.4, 950.2, 293.1]}, {"text": "", "bbox": [187.5, 299.3, 203.0, 324.9]}, {"text": "Personal auto – This business line includes personal auto coverages that protect against liability to", "bbox": [225.0, 301.2, 1109.1, 324.8]}, {"text": "others for both bodily injury and property damage, medical payments to insureds and occupants of", "bbox": [225.0, 324.8, 1108.4, 348.4]}, {"text": "their vehicle, physical damage to an insured’s own vehicle from collision and various other perils, and", "bbox": [225.0, 348.4, 1130.5, 372.1]}, {"text": "damages caused by uninsured motorists. In addition, many states require policies to provide first-party", "bbox": [225.0, 372.1, 1142.3, 395.7]}, {"text": "personal injury protection, frequently referred to as no-fault coverage.", "bbox": [225.1, 395.7, 853.0, 419.3]}, {"text": "", "bbox": [187.6, 422.4, 203.0, 448.0]}, {"text": "Homeowners – This business line includes homeowner coverages that protect against losses to", "bbox": [225.1, 424.3, 1077.5, 448.0]}, {"text": "dwellings and contents from a wide variety of perils, as well as liability arising out of personal activities", "bbox": [225.1, 447.8, 1144.0, 471.5]}, {"text": "both on and off the covered premises. The company also offers coverage for condominium unit owners", "bbox": [225.1, 471.4, 1144.6, 495.1]}, {"text": "and renters.", "bbox": [225.1, 495.1, 337.6, 518.7]}, {"text": "", "bbox": [187.6, 521.8, 203.0, 547.4]}, {"text": "Other personal lines – This includes the variety of other types of insurance products we offer to", "bbox": [225.1, 523.7, 1072.0, 547.3]}, {"text": "individuals such as dwelling fire, inland marine, personal umbrella liability and watercraft coverages.", "bbox": [225.1, 547.3, 1130.0, 571.0]}, {"text": "At year-end, we marketed personal lines insurance products through 1,059 of our 1,463 reporting agency", "bbox": [187.6, 577.2, 1130.9, 600.8]}, {"text": "locations in 29 of the 37 states in which we offer standard market commercial lines insurance.", "bbox": [187.6, 600.8, 1038.0, 624.5]}, {"text": "As discussed in Strategic Initiatives, Page 8, introducing personal lines to these agencies is one of the ways", "bbox": [187.6, 624.5, 1146.6, 648.1]}, {"text": "we intend to grow profitably in the next several years. The number of reporting agency locations in our", "bbox": [187.6, 648.1, 1098.6, 671.7]}, {"text": "10 highest volume states increased more than 5 percent to 660 in 2009 from 627 in 2008.", "bbox": [187.6, 671.7, 1009.8, 695.4]}, {"text": "In 2009, our 10 highest volume personal lines states generated 84.1 percent of our earned premiums", "bbox": [187.6, 701.6, 1101.0, 725.2]}, {"text": "compared with 85.1 percent in the prior year. Earned premiums in the 10 highest volume states declined", "bbox": [187.5, 725.2, 1128.5, 748.9]}, {"text": "1.7 percent in 2009 while increasing 5.9 percent in the remaining states.", "bbox": [187.5, 748.8, 849.2, 772.5]}, {"text": "Personal Lines Earned Premiums by State", "bbox": [187.5, 781.6, 626.6, 808.2]}, {"text": "New and renewal personal lines business reflects our risk-specific underwriting philosophy. Each agency", "bbox": [187.5, 1361.0, 1116.8, 1384.6]}, {"text": "selects personal lines business primarily from within the geographic territory that it serves, based on the", "bbox": [187.5, 1384.6, 1119.5, 1408.3]}, {"text": "agent’s knowledge of the risks in those communities or familiarity with the policyholder. Personal lines", "bbox": [187.5, 1408.3, 1107.4, 1431.9]}, {"text": "activities are supported by headquarters associates assigned to individual agencies. We now have", "bbox": [187.5, 1431.9, 1064.4, 1455.5]}, {"text": "seven full-time personal lines marketing representatives, who have underwriting authority and visit", "bbox": [187.5, 1455.5, 1070.4, 1479.2]}, {"text": "agencies on a regular basis. They reinforce the advantages of our personal lines products and offer training", "bbox": [187.5, 1479.2, 1144.6, 1502.8]}, {"text": "in the use of our processing system.", "bbox": [187.5, 1502.8, 512.6, 1526.4]}]}